chapters.title: How does the Bible describe a DREA "Simple" person?
In regards to crisis, what does the "simple" do? [Proverbs 22:3]
What will eventually happen to the "simple" and his REA simplicity? [Proverbs 22:3; 1:31 32]
Who does the "Slothful" person represent? DREA [Proverbs 24:30-34; Hebrews 2:3]
What did King David pray that God would keep him from? [Psalms 19:13]
What should every Christian brother seek to be to hisREA brother in regards to this coming crisis? [Genesis 4:8-10]
